'''佐匹克隆'''（{{lang-en|Zopiclone}}），又譯'''唑吡酮'''，暱稱'''安眠藥'''（{{lang-en|Imovane}}），香港濫用者俗稱其'''白瓜子'''、台灣稱'''樂比克'''<ref>{{cite journal |author= |title=What's wrong with prescribing hypnotics? |journal=Drug Ther Bull |volume=42 |issue=12 |pages=89–93 |date=December 2004 |pmid=15587763 |doi= 10.1136/dtb.2004.421289|url=}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Touitou Y |title=[Sleep disorders and hypnotic agents: medical, social and economical impact] |language=fr |journal=Ann Pharm Fr |volume=65 |issue=4 |pages=230–8 |date=July 2007 |pmid=17652991 |doi= |url=}}</ref>；是一种[[治疗|治疗]][[失眠|失眠]][[药物|药物]]。

佐匹克隆雖然在BZ<sub>1</sub>受體上產生作用，它卻不屬於[[苯二氮䓬類藥物|苯二氮{{僻字]]，而是一種[[環吡咯酮|環吡咯酮]]衍生物。

==不良反应==
副作用最多见于[[临床试验|临床试验]]中的味觉改变或[[味觉障碍|味觉障碍]]（比如口中含有苦味或金属味）通常这种味觉改变是短暂的，能持续至该药物的[[生物半衰期|半衰期]]过期。

佐匹克隆会引起类似于服用[[三唑仑|三唑仑]]之后造成的[[失忆症|失忆症]]类型的[[记忆损伤|记忆损伤]]<ref>{{cite journal |author=Gorenstein C, Tavares SM, Gentil V, Peres C, Moreno RA, Dreyfus JF |title=Psychophysiological effects and dose equivalence of zopiclone and triazolam administered to healthy volunteers. Methodological considerations |journal=Braz. J. Med. Biol. Res. |volume=23 |issue=10 |pages=941–51 |year=1990 |pmid=2101059 |doi= |url=}}</ref>和服用[[氟硝西泮|氟硝西泮]]之后导致的[[驾驶|驾驶]]技术降低，从而增加[[道路交通事故|道路交通事故]]的风险，恐怕是最严重的副作用。所以这类副作用并不是只服用'''佐匹克隆'''之后出现的。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Gustavsen I, Bramness JG, Skurtveit S, Engeland A, Neutel I, Mørland J |title=Road traffic accident risk related to prescriptions of the hypnotics zopiclone, zolpidem, flunitrazepam and nitrazepam |journal=Sleep Med. |volume=9 |issue=8 |pages=818–22 |date=December 2008 |pmid=18226959 |doi=10.1016/j.sleep.2007.11.011 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1389-9457(07)00424-8 |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2018-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818115316/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1389-9457(07)00424-8 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Verster JC, Veldhuijzen DS, Patat A, Olivier B, Volkerts ER |title=Hypnotics and driving safety: meta-analyses of randomized controlled trials applying the on-the-road driving test |journal=Curr Drug Saf |volume=1 |issue=1 |pages=63–71 |date=January 2006 |pmid=18690916 |doi= 10.2174/157488606775252674}}</ref>一项研究评估服用佐匹克隆对第二天驾驶技术的影响，之后发现驾驶技术的降低对社会的危害如同[[饮酒|酒后驾车]]。但某些安眠药例如[[扎来普隆|扎来普隆]]，对第二天的驾驶技术没有任何不利的影响。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Vermeeren A, Riedel WJ, van Boxtel MP, Darwish M, Paty I, Patat A |title=Differential residual effects of zaleplon and zopiclone on actual driving: a comparison with a low dose of alcohol |journal=Sleep |volume=25 |issue=2 |pages=224–31 |date=March 2002 |pmid=11905433 }}</ref>夜间长期服用其他[[非苯二氮䓬类药物|非苯二氮䓬类药物]]也会出现白天停药引发的[[焦虑|焦虑]]。<ref>{{ cite journal |pmid=2230061 |url= |format=PDF |date=Jul 1990 |author=Fontaine, R; Beaudry, P; Le, Morvan, P; Beauclair, L; Chouinard, G |title=Zopiclone and triazolam in insomnia associated with generalized anxiety disorder: a placebo-controlled evaluation of efficacy and daytime anxiety |volume=5 |issue=3 |pages=173–183 |issn=0268-1315 |journal=International clinical psychopharmacology |doi=10.1097/00004850-199007000-00002 }}</ref>

===比较常见的===
*'''胃肠道反应'''：味觉紊乱（如口中的苦味和金属味），[[口腔干燥|口腔干燥]]。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=6996815 |url= |year=1980 |author=Giercksky, Ke; Wickstrom, E |title=A dose-response study in situational insomnia with zopiclone, a new tranquilizer |volume=3 |issue=1 |pages=21–7 |issn=0149-2918 |journal=Clinical therapeutics  }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Ratrema M, Guy C, Nelva A, et al. |title=[Drug-induced taste disorders: analysis of the French Pharmacovigilance Database and literature review] |language=fr |journal=Therapie |volume=56 |issue=1 |pages=41–50 |year=2001 |pmid=11322016 |doi= |url=}}</ref>
*'''神经系统'''：中断[[REM睡眠|REM睡眠]]，[[复视|双重影像]]，[[嗜睡|嗜睡]]，记忆损伤，视觉空间减值，[[晕眩|晕眩]]，[[头痛|头痛]]，[[疲劳|疲劳]]以及[[情绪波动|情绪波动]]。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=7188378 |year=1982 |author=Nicholson, An; Stone, Bm |title=Zopiclone: sleep and performance studies in healthy man. |volume=17 Suppl 2 |issue= |pages=92–7 |issn=0020-8272 |journal=International pharmacopsychiatry }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pmid=6152563 |year=1984 |author=Subhan, Z; Hindmarch, I |title=Effects of zopiclone and benzodiazepine hypnotics on search in short-term memory. |volume=12 |issue=4 |pages=244–8 |issn=0302-282X |journal=Neuropsychobiology |url= |doi=10.1159/000118146 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pmid=6529528 |date=Dec 1984 |author=Channer, Ks; Dent, M; Roberts, Cj |title=The effect of posture at the time of administration on the central depressant effects of the new hypnotic zopiclone. |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-of-clinical-pharmacology_1984-12_18_6/page/879 |volume=18 |issue=6 |pages=879–86 |issn=0306-5251 |pmc=1463687 |journal=British Journal of Clinical Pharmacology |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2125.1984.tb02559.x}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pmid=3521857 |url= |year=1986 |author=Monchesky, Tc; Billings, Bj; Phillips, R |title=Zopiclone: a new nonbenzodiazepine hypnotic used in general practice. |volume=8 |issue=3 |pages=283–91 |issn=0149-2918 |journal=Clinical therapeutics }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Bocca ML, Denise P |title=Residual effects of hypnotics on disengagement of spatial attention |journal=J. Psychopharmacol. (Oxford) |volume=14 |issue=4 |pages=401–5 |year=2000 |pmid=11198059 |doi= 10.1177/026988110001400409|url=http://jop.sagepub.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=11198059}}</ref>

===不太常见的===
*'''胃肠道反应'''：[[胃灼热|胃灼热]]，[[便秘|便秘]]，[[腹泻|腹泻]]，[[恶心|恶心]]，[[舌苔|舌苔]]，[[口臭|口臭]]，[[食欲减退|食欲减退]]或[[食欲增加|食欲增加]]，[[呕吐|呕吐]]，腹部疼痛，[[消化不良|消化不良]]，[[脱水|脱水]]，[[味觉异常|味觉异常]]。
*'''心血管'''：老年患者用药出现[[心悸|心悸]]。
*'''皮肤'''：[[风疹|风疹]]，胳膊与腿有刺痛感。
*'''神经系统'''：[[激动|激动]]，<ref>{{cite journal |author=Moloney I, Breen EG, El Hassan H, Kelly BD |title=Extreme agitation occurring with zopiclone |journal=Ir Med J |volume=100 |issue=6 |page=511 |date=June 2007 |pmid=17668690 |doi= |url=}}</ref>[[焦虑|焦虑]]，[[失忆|失忆]]（包括[[逆向失憶症|逆向失憶症]]遗忘和[[順向失憶症|順向失憶症]]），[[头晕|头晕]]，[[乏力|乏力]]，[[嗜睡|嗜睡]]，[[虚弱|虚弱]]，[[兴奋|兴奋]]或[[烦躁不安|烦躁不安]]，[[醉态|醉态]]，[[忧郁|忧郁]]，[[梦游|梦游]]，<ref>{{cite journal |author=Ferentinos P, Paparrigopoulos T |title=Zopiclone and sleepwalking |journal=Int. J. Neuropsychopharmacol. |volume=12 |issue=1 |pages=141–2 |date=February 2009 |pmid=18925983 |doi=10.1017/S1461145708009541 |url=http://journals.cambridge.org/abstract_S1461145708009541}}</ref>[[协调异常|协调异常]]，[[肌无力|肌无力]]，乱讲话，[[行为障碍|行为障碍]]，[[易激惹|易激惹]]，[[幻觉|幻觉]]，[[失眠症反弹|失眠症反弹]]，[[噩梦|噩梦]]，轻度[[躁狂|躁狂]]。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=3679064 |url= |year=1987 |author=Warot, D; Bensimon, G; Danjou, P; Puech, Aj |title=Comparative effects of zopiclone, triazolam and placebo on memory and psychomotor performance in healthy volunteers. |volume=1 |issue=2 |pages=145–52 |issn=0767-3981 |journal=Fundamental & clinical pharmacology |doi=10.1111/j.1472-8206.1987.tb00553.x }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Fava GA |title=Amnestic syndrome induced by zoplclone |journal=Eur. J. Clin. Pharmacol. |volume=50 |issue=6 |page=509 |year=1996 |pmid=8858280 |doi= 10.1007/s002280050149|url=}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Silva A, Collao A, Orellana M, Meléndez J, Caviedes P, Cárdenas AM |title=Zopiclone, but not brotizolam, impairs memory storage during sleep |journal=Neurosci. Res. |volume=47 |issue=2 |pages=241–3 |date=October 2003 |pmid=14512149 |doi=10.1016/S0168-0102(03)00170-6 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0168010203001706 |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2018-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623050024/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0168010203001706 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。也可能发生[[精神错乱|精神错乱]]，但该情况主要见于老年人。<ref>{{cite journal |author=David M, Breton JL, Guy I, Vandel S |title=[Zopiclone and delirium: a case report] |language=fr |journal=Therapie |volume=53 |issue=1 |pages=78–80 |year=1998 |pmid=9773104 |doi= |url=}}</ref>
*'''其他'''：[[视力模糊|视力模糊]]，[[尿频|尿频]]，夜尿多。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Hussain N, MacKinnon M, Akbari A |title=Zopiclone-induced acute interstitial nephritis |journal=Am. J. Kidney Dis. |volume=41 |issue=5 |pages=E17 |date=May 2003 |pmid=12778435 |doi=10.1016/S0272-6386(03)00382-2 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0272638603002130 |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924125652/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0272638603002130 }}</ref>

===耐药性，依赖性和戒断反应===
佐匹克隆最初被宣称是比传统的[[苯二氮䓬類藥物|苯二氮䓬類藥物]]更不容易产生依赖与戒断反应的药物，然而佐匹克隆可能比传统的[[苯二氮䓬類藥物|苯二氮䓬類藥物]]有更大的潜在依赖性，并已经被形容为“苯二氮䓬類藥物的变相”。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Bramness JG |author2=Olsen H.  | year = 1998 | title = [Adverse effects of zopiclone] | journal = Tidsskrift for den Norske laegeforening. | volume = 118 | issue = 13 | pages = 2029–32 | pmid = 9656789 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Luty S, Sellman D |title=Imovane—a benzodiazepine in disguise |journal=N. Z. Med. J. |volume=106 | issue=959 |page=293 |date=July 1993 |pmid=8321452 |doi= |url=}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Deveaux M, Chèze M, Pépin G |title=The role of liquid chromatography-tandem mass spectrometry (LC-MS/MS) to test blood and urine samples for the toxicological investigation of drug-facilitated crimes |journal=Ther Drug Monit |volume=30 |issue=2 |pages=225–8 |date=April 2008 |pmid=18367985 |doi=10.1097/FTD.0b013e3181676186 |url=http://meta.wkhealth.com/pt/pt-core/template-journal/lwwgateway/media/landingpage.htm?an=00007691-200804000-00015 |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2013-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601021233/http://meta.wkhealth.com/pt/pt-core/template-journal/lwwgateway/media/landingpage.htm?an=00007691-200804000-00015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>佐匹克隆应尽量避免在多数情况下长期使用，如果突然停药尤其是长时间服用高剂量之后停药，最严重的时候会导致患者[[癫痫|癫痫]]与[[谵妄|谵妄]]（[[精神错乱|精神错乱]]）。<ref>{{cite journal |author= | title = Hypnotic dependence: zolpidem and zopiclone too |journal=Prescrire Int |volume=10 |issue=51 |page=15 |date=February 2001 | pmid = 11503851 | doi= |url=}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Wong CP, Chiu PK, Chu LW |title=Zopiclone withdrawal: an unusual cause of delirium in the elderly |journal=Age Ageing |volume=34 |issue=5 |pages=526–7 |date=September 2005 |pmid=16107464 |doi=10.1093/ageing/afi132 |url=http://ageing.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/34/5/526 |format=PDF |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2006-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060302041217/http://ageing.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/34/5/526 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在出版物《[[英国医学杂志|英国医学杂志]]》中没有给出任何可以证明“佐匹克隆依赖性很小”的证据。事实上[[生理依赖|生理依赖]]、[[康乐滥用|康乐滥用]]和成瘾后的戒断症状相似，这类症状在[[苯二氮平类药物|苯二氮平类药物]]停药的时候经常遇到。戒断症状包括[[焦虑|焦虑]]、心跳加速、[[震颤|震颤]]、[[盗汗|盗汗]]、[[脸红|脸红]]、[[心悸|心悸]]，也会出现失眠加重的情况。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Jones IR, Sullivan G |title=Physical dependence on zopiclone: case reports |journal=BMJ |volume= 316 |issue=7125 |page=117 |date=January 1998 |pmid=9462317 |doi= 10.1136/bmj.316.7125.117|url=http://bmj.com/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=9462317 |pmc= 2665371}}</ref>2007年美国曾经报道过有人在佐匹克隆戒断排毒期间发生[[抽搐|抽搐]]反应，但该人是长期服用高剂量佐匹克隆的[[滥用药物|滥用药物]]者。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=1754610 |url= |date=Jul 1991 |author=Aranko, K; Henriksson, M; Hublin, C; Seppäläinen, Am |title=Misuse of zopiclone and convulsions during withdrawal. |volume=24 |issue=4 |pages=138–40 |issn=0176-3679 |journal= Pharmacopsychiatry |doi=10.1055/s-2007-1014457 }}</ref>

如果连续服用佐匹克隆不到14天或者只是偶尔服用佐匹克隆，那么产生依赖性的风险比较低。<ref>{{cite journal | pmid = 3326116 | url = | year=1987 |author=Anderson, Aa |title=Zopiclone and nitrazepam: a multicenter placebo controlled comparative study of efficacy and tolerance in insomniac patients in general practice. |volume=10 Suppl 1 |issue= |pages=54–62 |issn=0161-8105 |journal=Sleep }}</ref>然而这在一项仅服用7晚低剂量佐匹克隆的研究里是受争议的。这项研究发现佐匹克隆停药会引起显著[[反跳性失眠|反跳性失眠]]。此外，[[苯二氮䓬類藥物|苯二氮䓬類藥物]]之一的[[咪达唑仑|咪达唑仑]]服用7夜停药之后无反跳性失眠，这表明佐匹克隆比[[苯二氮䓬類藥物|苯二氮䓬類藥物]]有更明显的[[耐药性|耐药性]]和依赖性的问题。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Mendelson WB, Jain B |title = An assessment of short-acting hypnotics |journal=Drug Saf |volume=13 |issue=4 |pages=257–70 |date=October 1995 |pmid=8573298 |doi= 10.2165/00002018-199513040-00005|url=}}</ref>长期服用佐匹克隆而导致依赖的患者突然停药会发生严重的戒断症状如[[精神错乱|精神错乱]]，所以不应该突然停药。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Harter C, Piffl-Boniolo E, Rave-Schwank M |title=[Development of drug withdrawal delirium after dependence on zolpidem and zoplicone] |language=de |journal = Psychiatr Prax |volume=26 |issue=6 |page=309 |date=November 1999 |pmid=10627964 |doi= |url=}}</ref>如果佐匹克隆已经服用超过数周，之后的服用药量应该逐渐降低。或者直接改用[[等效剂量|等效剂量]]的[[地西泮|地西泮]]（俗称「安定」），因为[[地西泮|地西泮]]具有更长的半衰期，所以会使停药更容易。然后过几个月再逐渐减少其用量，以避免极严重又极易导致患者烦恼的停药症状（例如[[内坐立不安|内坐立不安]]、[[精神运动性激越|精神运动性激越]]、[[腹痛|腹痛]]、[[高血压|高血压]]、[[幻觉|幻觉]]、[[癫痫|癫痫]]、[[焦虑症|焦虑症]]、[[抑郁症|抑郁症]]、[[精神病|精神病]]等）。需要注意的是如果停药做得太急剧的话，停药症状可能持续长达两年。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sanofi-aventis.ca/products/en/imovane.pdf |title=IMOVANE (zopiclone) Tablets, 5.0 mg and 7.5 mg |author=sanofi-aventis Canada Inc |authorlink=sanofi-aventis |date=October 30, 2008 |format=PDF |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314200135/http://sanofi-aventis.ca/products/en/imovane.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author=Kahlert I |author2=Brüne M  |date=June 2001 | title=[A case of primary zopiclone dependence] | journal=Dtsch Med Wochenschr | volume=126 | issue=22 | pages=653–4 | pmid=11450624 | doi=10.1055/s-2001-14488 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.benzo.org.uk/manual/ |title=BENZODIAZEPINES: HOW THEY WORK AND HOW TO WITHDRAW |author=Professor Heather Ashton |accessdate=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2019-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507112228/https://www.benzo.org.uk/manual/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

连续4星期晚上服用佐匹克隆之后，部分患者在白天停药的时候出现了相关的[[焦虑|焦虑]]症状。然而白天停药引发的焦虑在[[三唑仑|三唑仑]]药物中并没有那么激烈，反而症状时间更短暂。这令那些由于白天停药而引发[[焦虑|焦虑]]的患者更为愤怒。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=2230061 |url= |format=PDF |date=Jul 1990 |author=Fontaine, R; Beaudry, P; Le, Morvan, P; Beauclair, L; Chouinard, G |title=Zopiclone and triazolam in insomnia associated with generalized anxiety disorder: a placebo-controlled evaluation of efficacy and daytime anxiety. |volume=5 |issue=3 |pages=173–83 |issn=0268-1315 |journal=International clinical psychopharmacology |doi=10.1097/00004850-199007000-00002 }}</ref>

根据[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]（[[英语|英语]]：World Health Organisation）的说法，虽然佐匹克隆的分子不是[[苯二氮卓|苯二氮卓]]，但是其与[[苯二氮卓类药物|苯二氮卓类药物]]非常相似。世界卫生组织还指出，佐匹克隆与[[苯二氮卓类药物|苯二氮卓类药物]]具有[[交叉耐受性|交叉耐受性]]，服用期间也可替换为其他的[[苯二氮卓类药物|苯二氮卓类药物]]。[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]在对佐匹克隆的审阅中发现戒断症状通常发生在这两种药物的其中一种服用剂量过大或者长时间服用佐匹克隆。其报道的戒断症状包括[[焦虑|焦虑]]、[[心动过速|心动过速]]、[[震颤|震颤]]、[[盗汗|盗汗]]，[[失眠|失眠]]反弹、[[抽搐|抽搐]]、[[心悸|心悸]]和[[脸红|脸红]]。<ref name=whoaoz>{{cite web | url = http://www.who.int/medicines/areas/quality_safety/4.6ZopicloneCritReview.pdf | title = World Health Organisation - Assessment of Zopiclone | author = WHO | authorlink = World Health Organisation | year = 2006 | format = PDF | publisher = who.int | accessdate = 2014-08-27 | archive-date = 2015-01-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150131215218/http://www.who.int/medicines/areas/quality_safety/4.6ZopicloneCritReview.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==特别注意事项==
服用佐匹克隆的时候应当避免饮用[[酒精|酒精]]以及含有酒精的食物、饮料，例如当酒精和佐匹克隆一起服用时会互相增强效果，同时也会增加对药物的依赖。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Kuitunen T |author2=Mattila MJ |author3=Seppala T  |title=Actions and interactions of hypnotics on human performance: single doses of zopiclone, triazolam, and alcohol |volume=5 |issue=Suppl 2 |pages=115–30 |date=April 1990 |pmid=2201724 |journal=Int Clin Psychopharmacol }}</ref>

肝病患者对佐匹克隆的戒除要比普通患者缓慢，除了一些对药物的[[药理作用|药理作用]]有丰富经验的患者。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=6626417 |date=Sep 1983 |author=Parker, G; Roberts, Cj |title=Plasma concentrations and central nervous system effects of the new hypnotic agent zopiclone in patients with chronic liver disease. |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-of-clinical-pharmacology_1983-09_16_3/page/259 |volume=16 |issue=3 |pages=259–65 |issn=0306-5251 |pmc=1428012 |journal=British Journal of Clinical Pharmacology |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2125.1983.tb02159.x}}</ref>

佐匹克隆服用之后也会使患者走路晃晃悠悠，老年患者服用之后也会增加摔倒的概率。多数老年人若不慎摔倒也会导致死亡，所以老年人服用之后应避免长时间的站立与走动。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid=8127419 |url= |year=1994 |author=Tada, K; Sato, Y; Sakai, T; Ueda, N; Kasamo, K; Kojima, T |title=Effects of zopiclone, triazolam, and nitrazepam on standing steadiness. |volume=29 |issue=1 |pages=17–22 |issn=0302-282X |journal=Neuropsychobiology |doi=10.1159/000119057 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Allain H, Bentué-Ferrer D, Tarral A, Gandon JM |title=Effects on postural oscillation and memory functions of a single dose of zolpidem 5 mg, zopiclone 3.75 mg and lormetazepam 1 mg in elderly healthy subjects. A randomized, cross-over, double-blind study versus placebo |journal=Eur. J. Clin. Pharmacol. |volume=59 |issue=3 |pages=179–88 |date=July 2003 |pmid=12756510 |doi=10.1007/s00228-003-0591-5 |url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/kun2pr7nyfv8ua00/fulltext.pdf |format=PDF |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2020-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328180702/http://www.springerlink.com/content/kun2pr7nyfv8ua00/fulltext.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Antai-Otong D |title=The art of prescribing. Risks and benefits of non-benzodiazepine receptor agonists in the treatment of acute primary insomnia in older adults |journal=Perspect Psychiatr Care |volume=42 |issue=3 |pages=196–200 |date=August 2006 |pmid=16916422 |doi=10.1111/j.1744-6163.2006.00070.x |url=http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/journal/118727940/abstract |access-date=2014-08-27 |archive-date=2020-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328180703/http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/journal/118727940/abstract |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

一些患有[[重症肌无力|重症肌无力]]或者由于严重的[[慢性支气管炎|慢性支气管炎]]、[[肺气肿|肺气肿]]等肺部疾病导致[[呼吸储备|呼吸储备]]较差的患者，或者患有睡眠[[呼吸暂停|呼吸暂停]]症的患者不宜服用佐匹克隆，患有[[甲状腺异常|甲状腺异常]]且没有经过任何治疗的患者也不宜服用。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Upfal |first1=Jonathan |title=The Australian Drug Guide |edition=5 |year=2000 |origyear=1991 |publisher=Bookman Press Pty Ltd |location=Melbourne |isbn=1-86395-170-9 |page=743}}</ref>

== 药物滥用 ==
在美国，佐匹克隆是著名的[[吸毒|吸毒]]者滥用药物之一，而且他们通常是从医院获取药物。（美国某戒毒所发现5.1%的吸毒者在其治疗中心报告了他们的佐匹克隆上瘾）{{citation needed|date=September 2012}}

滥用者经常与酒精饮料一起服用以达到安眠药与酒精相结合的兴奋感。患者滥用药物的行为同样存在会产生药物依赖的风险，即使以后将服用量减小，但由于持续服药时间过长，戒断症状在短时间内也不会消失。所以一些医药公司与相关人员建议处方药量不得高于7至10天的服用量，原因就是担心[[物质依赖|物质依赖]]、[[药物耐受|药物耐受]]和[[身体依赖|身体依赖]]。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Cimolai N |title=Zopiclone: is it a pharmacologic agent for abuse? |journal=Can Fam Physician |volume=53 |issue=12 |pages=2124–9 |date=December 2007 |pmid=18077750 |pmc=2231551 |doi= }}</ref> 

滥用佐匹克隆与酒精两类药物会导致服药后的[[兴奋|兴奋]]，导致患者直接将该药物当作[[娱乐性药物|娱乐性药物]]进行滥用，同时也会长期违背医嘱用量去服用药物。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Griffiths RR, Johnson MW |title=Relative abuse liability of hypnotic drugs: a conceptual framework and algorithm for differentiating among compounds |journal=J Clin Psychiatry |volume=66 Suppl 9 |issue= |pages=31–41 |year=2005 |pmid=16336040 |doi= |url=}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Hoffmann F, Pfannkuche M, Glaeske G |title=[High usage of zolpidem and zopiclone. Cross-sectional study using claims data] |language=de |journal=Nervenarzt |volume=79 |issue=1 |pages=67–72 |date=January 2008 |pmid=17457554 |doi=10.1007/s00115-007-2280-6}}</ref>一些曾有过[[滥用药物|滥用药物]]或者曾经患有[[精神疾病|精神疾病]]的患者服用高剂量佐匹克隆可能会增加滥用药物的风险。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Ströhle A, Antonijevic IA, Steiger A, Sonntag A |title=[Dependency of non-benzodiazepine hypnotics. Two case reports] |language=de |journal=Nervenarzt |volume=70 |issue=1 |pages=72–5 |date=January 1999 |pmid=10087521 |doi= 10.1007/s001150050403|url= }}</ref>

==在生物体液中的检测==
佐匹克隆在人体中的含量可用[[色谱法|色谱法]]在[[血液|血液]]，[[血浆|血浆]]或[[尿液|尿液]]当中进行测定。在正常的用量中，药物在人体血浆中的含量通常低于100 μg/L（[[微克|微克]]/升），但是在血浆当中药物的含量超出100 μg/L尤其是发生在汽车驾驶员身上的时候，会影响他们的驾驶能力。一些服药之后导致急性中毒的患者的含量通常在1000 μg/L以上。有[[尸检|尸检]]报告指出一些由于[[急性药物中毒|急性药物中毒]]的死者的血液含药浓度通常在0.4-3.9 mg/L（[[毫克|毫克]]/升）。<ref>Kratzsch C, Tenberken O, Peters FT et al. Screening, library-assisted identification, and validated quantification of 23 benzodiazepines, flumazenil, zaleplone, zolpidem, and zopiclone in plasma by liquid chromatography/mass spectrometry with atmospheric pressure chemical ionization. J. Mass Spec. 39: 856-872, 2004.</ref><ref>Gustavsen I, Al-Sammurraie M, Mørland J, Bramness JG. Impairment related to blood drug concentrations of zopiclone and zolpidem compared with alcohol in apprehended drivers. Accid. Anal. Prev. 41: 462-466, 2009.</ref><ref>R. Baselt, ''Disposition of Toxic Drugs and Chemicals in Man'', 8th edition, Biomedical Publications, Foster City, CA, 2008, pp. 1677-1679.</ref>

